-- Conergy to Sell 30% Stake to Chinese Solar Company, FTD Reports
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-05-09T19:48:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-09/conergy-to-sell-30-stake-to-chinese-solar-company-ftd-reports.html
Conergy AG (CGYK)  is on the verge of selling
a 30 percent stake to a Chinese solar company, the  Financial
Times Deutschland  reported in a preview of an article to be
published tomorrow, citing an unidentified person with knowledge
of the deal.  The only doubt remaining is when the deal will be
completed, the newspaper said, citing the person, who declined
to name the buyer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
